quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,87,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e am, yehee tefon fii Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on. Wata on taЖҙo e yurmeende Alla. Ko fii, taЖҙotaako e yurmeende Alla si wanaa yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  12,88,"Nde Й“e naatunoo ka makko [kanko Yuusufa], Й“e wi'i: \"Ko an yo laamЙ—o, lorra heЙ“ii men memen e Й“eynguure amen; men ardii e sil'a jaasuЙ—o. Hunnan men Й“etu ngun, sakko-Й—aa e amen. Pellet, Alla yoЙ“ay sakkotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,89,"O maaki: \"Enee, on annditii ko waЙ—unoЙ—on Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on kon tuma nde wonunoЙ—on majjuЙ“e"
  12,90,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Kere ko an woni Yuusufa?\" O maaki: \"Ko min woni Yuusufa. Oo Й—oo ko miГұam. GomЙ—ii Alla moЖҙЖҙike e amen. Ko fii, mo gomЙ—ii o muГұГұike, pellet, Alla yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondiri Alla, Alla Й“urnii ma e amen, men woniino woopuЙ“e"
  12,92,"O maaki: \"Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde! Yo Alla yawtan on. Ko Kano woni MoЖҙЖҙo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  12,93,"Yahdee e oo dolokke am Й—oo, werloЙ—on mo ka yeeso baaben am: o wattinay yi'oowo. Addanon lam Й“eynguure mon nden Й“e denndaangal"
  12,94,"Nde seteeЙ“e Й“en seerti [yalti Misra]ben maЙ“Й“e maaki: \"Min miЙ—o heЙ“a balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo on Й—aytinam"
  12,95,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men woondirii Alla, an hiЙ—a e majjere maaЙ—a Й“ooyunde nden"
